<br>
JAKE appears, looks at her door.<br>
<br>
JAKE:<br>
<br>
Oh no...<br>
<br>
((JAKE runs right THROUGH the door. CAMERA closeup on name on mailbox &quot;Forrester, Sylvia&quot;))<br>
<br>
<br>
INTERIOR: SYLVIA'S APARTMENT<br>
<br>
JAKE runs through the apartment, searching for SYLVIA. He finally comes to a dark bedroom, where SYLVIA is in front of a mirror, not looking in it, putting her earrings into a box. WICKS is standing behind her, a long butcher knife raised.<br>
<br>
<br>
JAKE:<br>
<br>
NOOOOOOOOO!<br>
<br>
<br>
(SYLVIA'S head snaps up. She has heard him, even tho he does not reflect int he mirror. But WICKS does reflect, and she sees him. She spins around and dodges to the side as WICKS buries the knife into the wood bureau. SYLVIA hits WICKS with thelamp by the bed. It shatters over his head and he staggers. SYLVIA tries to get away, but WICKS grabs her, hands locking around her throat, as he tries to strangle her.)<br>
<br>
(SYLVIA gropes and finds the knife. She pulls it free of the bureau)<br>
<br>
(WICKS tightens, intent on killing her)<br>
<br>
(SYLVIA staps him in the back, the knife coming through him and almost stabbing herself in the process)<br>
<br>
(WICKS shudders, a look of shock on his face, and dies)<br>
<br>
(SYLVIA runs from the room)<br>
<br>
<br>
(WICK'S SPIRIT rises from the body. JAKE raises the doors. WICKS looks at JAKE, smiles and begins walking toward the white door)<br>
<br>
((SUDDENLY, JAKE reaches for WICK'S shoulder, and spins him around, so WICK'S back is to the black door))<br>
<br>
<br>
JAKE:<br>
<br>
Fuck the rules.<br>
<br>
<br>
(JAKE punches WICKS in the face. WICKS staggers back, splintering open the Black Door. He is sucked through and gone.)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
INTERIOR: SOMMA'S HOSPITAL ROOM<br>
<br>
JAKE appears next to SOMMA'S bed. He pulls the old man from his body urgently.<br>
<br>
JAKE: Let's do it. If I see her again, I won't be able to help myself.<br>
<br>
<br>
SOMMA:<br>
<br>
Do you know how?<br>
<br>
<br>
JAKE:<br>
<br>
I think I'll manage, it's all in the mind.<br>
<br>
<br>
SOMMA:<br>
<br>
Then let's begin.<br>
<br>
<br>
(Scene fades, then comes back in. SOMMA, in reaper's robes, stares at his own body as JAKE'S imagine, which is superimposed over it, fades from view.)<br>
<br>
<br>
SOMMA:<br>
<br>
Good luck, son. I hope you have the will to wake up.<br>
<br>
<br>
((The body on the bed does not respond))<br>
